dataKey.description: Name of the field that uniquely identifies the a record in the data.
dataKey.description_zh: 唯一标识数据中 a 记录的字段的名称。

metaKeySelection.description:
Defines whether metaKey is requred or not for the selection.
When true metaKey needs to be pressed to select or unselect an item and
when set to false selection of each item can be toggled individually. On touch enabled devices, metaKeySelection is turned off automatically.
metaKeySelection.description_zh:
定义是否需要 metaKey 进行选择。
当需要按下 true metaKey 来选择或取消选择项目时，并且
设置为 false 时，可以单独选择每个项目。在支持触摸的设备上，metaKeySelection 会自动关闭。

listStyle.description: Inline style of the the list element.

responsive.description: Whether the list optimizes layout based on screen size.
responsive.description_zh: 列表是否根据屏幕尺寸优化布局。

breakpoint.description: The breakpoint to define the maximum width boundary when responsiveness is enabled.
breakpoint.description_zh: 启用响应能力时用于定义最大宽度边界的断点。

stripedRows.description: Whether to displays rows with alternating colors.
stripedRows.description_zh: 是否显示颜色交替的行。

tabindex.description: Index of the element in tabbing order.
tabindex.description_zh: 按 Tab 键顺序排列的元素索引。

listProps.description: Used to pass all properties of the HTMLAttributes to the list element.
listProps.description_zh: 用于将 HTMLAttributes 的所有属性传递给 list 元素。

moveUpButtonProps.description: Used to pass all properties of the HTMLButtonElement to the move up button inside the component.
moveUpButtonProps.description_zh: 用于将 HTMLButtonElement 的所有属性传递给组件内的上移按钮。

moveTopButtonProps.description: Used to pass all properties of the HTMLButtonElement to the move top button inside the component.
moveTopButtonProps.description_zh: 用于将 HTMLButtonElement 的所有属性传递给组件内的“移动顶部”按钮。

moveDownButtonProps.description: Used to pass all properties of the HTMLButtonElement to the move down button inside the component.
moveDownButtonProps.description_zh: 用于将 HTMLButtonElement 的所有属性传递给组件内的下移按钮。

moveBottomButtonProps.description: Used to pass all properties of the HTMLButtonElement to the move bottom button inside the component.
moveBottomButtonProps.description_zh: 用于将 HTMLButtonElement 的所有属性传递给组件内的移动底部按钮。

aria-label.description: Defines a string value that labels an interactive list element.
aria-label.description_zh: 定义一个字符串值，该值标记交互式列表元素。

aria-labelledby.description: Identifier of the underlying list element.
aria-labelledby.description_zh: 基础列表元素的标识符。

pt.description: Used to pass attributes to DOM elements inside the component.
pt.description_zh: 用于将属性传递给组件内部的 DOM 元素。

ptOptions.description: Used to configure passthrough(pt) options of the component.
ptOptions.description_zh: 用于配置组件的直通 （pt） 选项。

unstyled.description: When enabled, it removes component related styles in the core.
unstyled.description_zh: 启用后，它会删除核心中与组件相关的样式。

events.name: reorder
events.description: Callback to invoke when the list is reordered.
events.description_zh: 在列表重新排序时调用的回调。

events.name: selection-change
events.description: Callback to invoke when selection changes.
events.description_zh: 在选择更改时调用的回调。
